    <ingredient>3 TBSP oregano </ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 TBSP basil</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBSP dill</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 TBSP onion powder (optional)</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 TBSP garlic powder </ingredient>
    <ingredient>1/2 TBSP salt</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBSP pepper</ingredient>

    <step>
Add all ingredients to an airtight jar. Place lid on jar and shake well. Makes 1/2 cup, store out of light in pantry. Use generously on any meat or veggies - yum yum!
